ActFinancial Administration Act
Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of ANDREW J. KRIEGLER of Toronto, Ontario, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Angela Tu Weissenberger, whose term has expired.
